==Overhead dialogue==
===Picking up a load from the [[Digsite]]===
* '''Dig Site workman:''' {{overhead|Got another load for ya!}}
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Great, just what my arms need!}}

===Taking a break while travelling to [[Varrock]], just before reaching the gate===
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Ohhh, time for a break.}}
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Time I got moving...}}

===Upon reaching the gate next to the [[museum guard]] after leaving the Digsite===
* '''Museum Guard:''' {{overhead|Keep 'em coming!}}
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Bleah}}

===Upon reaching [[Varrock Museum]], while unloading the wheelbarrow near the Dig Site specimen rocks===
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Another lot for ya!}}
* '''[Sinco Doar/Tinse Torpe]:''' {{overhead|Alright, thanks!}}
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Off we go again!}}

===Upon leaving Varrock, near the guards stationed at the eastern exit===
* {{tact|A guard will be chosen at random to respond to the workman.}}
* {{tcond|If the chosen guard is not under attack from a player:}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|How's it going, officers?}}
** '''Guard:''' {{overhead|Another boring day.}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Nothing new there.}}
* {{tcond|If the chosen guard is under attack from a player:}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|How's it going, officers?}}
** '''Guard:''' {{overhead|I'm being slaughtered!}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Nothing new there.}}
* {{tcond|If all of the guards are currently dead:}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|How's it going, officers?}}
** '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Oh, they're all dead.}}

===Upon reaching the gate next to the [[museum guard]] after leaving Varrock===
* '''Museum Guard:''' {{overhead|Don't dawdle there!}}
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Yeah, yeah, I'm movin' guv.}}

===Taking a break while travelling to the Digsite===
* '''Workman:''' {{overhead|Hmm, time for a break.}}
